<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%= image_tag attachments['logo.png'].url, height: '30', width: '115' %>
    <p>
      To verify your account and start using Vizibid click the link below. If the link cannot be clicked, copy the URL below and paste it into the address bar of your browser.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= verify_url(@user.verification_token) %>
    </p>
    <% if @manual == true %>
      <h3>User Info</h3>
       Name: <%= @user.name %><br/>
       Email: <%= @user.email %><br/>
       Bar Number: <%= @user.bar_number %><br/>
       State: <%= @user.state_licensed %><br/>
    <% end %>
    <div>
      Vizibid is not a law firm and does not provide legal advice. Using the Vizibid websites and services or sending Vizibid an email does not constitute legal advice and does not create an attorney-client relationship. Vizibid provides all websites, services, information, tools, and licenses on an "as-is" basis.
    </div>
  </body>
</html>